---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import SiteNav from '../components/SiteNav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer';
---

<Layout
  title="Automation Programs"
  description="Replace repetitive processes with n8n, Netlify, and custom workflows tuned to your ops team."
>
  <SiteNav />

  <main class="bg-zinc-900">
    <section class="py-24 border-b border-zinc-800/60">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-8">
        <div class="max-w-3xl">
          <p class="uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 mb-4">
            automation
          </p>
          <h1 class="text-h1 font-bold text-zinc-50 mb-6">
            Automations that feel like an extra teammate
          </h1>
          <p class="text-lg text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">
            We design n8n and Netlify automation programs that handle the boring stuff—reporting, onboarding,
            follow-ups—while keeping humans in the driver’s seat. Everything is documented, observable, and ready
            for audits.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-24 bg-zinc-950 border-b border-zinc-800/60">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-zinc-50 mb-10">Automation menu</h2>
        <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
          <div class="card-slate">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-2">Sales & quoting</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
              Auto-generate proposals, route approvals, and sync updates back to CRM without the copy-paste grind.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="card-slate">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-2">Customer onboarding</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
              Collect docs, spin up accounts, assign tasks, and nudge teams when human touch is required.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="card-slate">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-2">Operations dashboards</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
              Pull from spreadsheets, ERPs, and APIs to build daily snapshots with alerts for outliers.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="card-slate">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-2">Revenue collection</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
              Trigger reminders, process payments, and reconcile ledgers with audit trails intact.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="card-slate">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-2">Internal comms</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
              Schedule updates, summarize meetings, and push highlights to Slack, Teams, or email digests.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="card-slate">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-2">Field service</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
              Log work orders, sync photos, and dispatch follow-up tasks so nothing slips through the cracks.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-24 border-b border-zinc-800/60">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-8">
        <div class="grid gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-zinc-50 mb-6">Our automation stack</h2>
            <ul class="space-y-4 text-sm text-zinc-300">
              <li><span class="font-semibold text-zinc-100">n8n:</span> Visual builders with TypeScript nodes for custom logic.</li>
              <li><span class="font-semibold text-zinc-100">Netlify Functions:</span> Lightweight serverless endpoints for quick integrations.</li>
              <li><span class="font-semibold text-zinc-100">Supabase & Firestore:</span> Secure storage for state, history, and analytics.</li>
              <li><span class="font-semibold text-zinc-100">Playwright:</span> Browser automations for stubborn legacy apps.</li>
              <li><span class="font-semibold text-zinc-100">Observability:</span> Structured logging, dashboards, and alerting so ops can debug fast.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="card-slate space-y-4">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-50">Implementation process</h3>
            <ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-2 text-sm text-zinc-300">
              <li>Map the current workflow and turnaround expectations.</li>
              <li>Prototype the automation in a sandbox with sample data.</li>
              <li>Run a shadow period where humans review every action.</li>
              <li>Roll into production with monitoring and iterative tweaks.</li>
            </ol>
            <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
              Typical timeline is 10 business days from kickoff to production for a single workflow lane.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-24 bg-zinc-950 border-b border-zinc-800/60">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-zinc-50 mb-8">Runbook & support</h2>
        <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
          <div class="card-slate">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-2">Documented playbooks</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
              You get editable runbooks, diagrams, and rollback steps so the program can live beyond any one vendor.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="card-slate">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-2">Training included</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
              We onboard your operators, teach them how to request new automations, and set up feedback loops.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="card-slate">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-2">Fixed monthly support</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
              Flat-rate plans cover monitoring, patching, and incremental tweaks so you can budget confidently.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="card-slate">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-2">Compliance friendly</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
              Audit logs, access controls, and approval trails keep legal and finance teams comfortable.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-24">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-8">
        <div class="grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-2">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-zinc-50 mb-4">Ready to map an automation trail?</h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 mb-6">
              Bring one workflow, we’ll show you a path to full automation plus the reporting leadership wants.
            </p>
            <a href="/#contact" class="btn-primary">Request an automation audit</a>
          </div>
          <div class="card-slate space-y-4">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-50">FAQ</h3>
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm text-zinc-300 font-medium">How do you price automations?</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">Flat cost per workflow lane + optional monthly retainer for support.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm text-zinc-300 font-medium">Can you integrate with legacy systems?</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">Yes—screen automation, CSV bridges, and lightweight APIs keep everything talking.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm text-zinc-300 font-medium">How do we request changes?</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">Submit tweaks via a shared board; most updates ship within 48 hours.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
